desc_short	-----								Shadows Peak is a story-driven, atmospheric, open-world horror game focused on exploration. You play as a writer who has decided to visit a mysterious place called Shadows Peak to gather materials for a new book about legends. Be warned, Shadows Peak will not hold your hand.							
